      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-caliber E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This S65 V8 power unit has been meticulously maintained with shortened OCI intervals using only Liqui Moly 10W-60. Rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014the common failure points\u2014have been proactively addressed and documented. The chassis remains laser-straight with zero subframe deflection, riding on an EDC-tuned suspension that offers surgical precision through the twisties. The DCT transmission logic has been flashed to GTS specifications for lightning-fast shifts and optimized clamping force. This is a turn-key machine for the discerning purist who demands peak volumetric efficiency and uncompromised structural integrity. No leaks, no codes, just pure mechanical harmony.",
      "price": 48900.0,
